title: Khonsu Clock Lamp (Wireless Charging)
body_html: When decorating your home, it’s always considered a win-win when something is both fashionable and functional. Take the Khonsu Clock Lamp for example: Crafted from metal, it boasts a round silhouette, so it’s sure to make a bold statement on any bare space in your abode plus it functions as a lamp and wireless charger at the same time! A decorative wall clock without numbers can bring a different style to your home!

title: Light of Life Lamp
body_html:
Say hello to your new favourite home decor.

The Light of Life exhibits a thin, cherry wood shade, and brightness that can be smoothly adjusted via touch controls on the base.

In addition, the base of the lamp also has an integrated wireless charging pad, so you can charge any phone wirelessly!

This stunning lamp even comes with a built-in neodymium Bluetooth speaker. Just pair your device to the lamp, and play your favourite music wirelessly. You can even use the touch controls on the lamp to skip songs and adjust the volume.

title: Sands of Time Lamp
body_html: When styling your home, it’s definitely a win-win when you stumble upon something that is both fashionable and functional. The Sands of Time Lamp is crafted of metal with a beautiful round silhouette that boasts a relaxing moving sand art piece that changes daily and helps boost your intellectual thinking and mood. It's a designer masterpiece that's unique and perfect for any desk across your home. A decorative unique lamp like this can bring a different style to your home that can liven up your space!

title: Diamond Fever Square 3D Wall Panel
body_html:
Add architectural style to any wall quickly and affordably. Transforming a dull, boring space into a dynamic, aesthetic one in minutes with these sleek geometric wall panels. 

Improving the look and the feel of your space, our leather wall panels have a high-density foam filling that absorbs sound. They create an ambient sound level that adds to the opulence of your home or place of business.

They are easy to install with standard adhesives and choose our white panels to paint them any colour of the rainbow. 

*Available in 70+ colors and styles, If you’re interested in another color that’s not available please contact our customer service team at info@articture.com*

title: Mersenne Speaker Table
body_html:
An immersive and rich bluetooth speaker side table that delivers true 360° sound for consistent and amazing coverage without compromising function and style. The Mersenne is made to be placed in the centre of any room to amp and resonate music around your space for the best listening experience.

Featuring a smooth, round, fabric speaker body that allows a high-range bluetooth connection in an eye-catchy and compact height, measuring 25-inches high and 16-inches wide only.

title: Damascus Steel Knife Set (3 Piece Set)
body_html:
A knife can be more than just a tool. It can be art.

Rare blacksmiths in the Damascus region were regarded as the finest in the world for their unique technique of steel fabrication. Their methods were said to produce the most beautiful swords all over the world. By heating and folding the steel over many times, the blade becomes stronger, more ductile, and also incredibly beautiful. The Japanese still practice this tradition in their Chef Knives today.

Featuring a geometric ebony wood handle, our knife set includes 3 pieces that give you all that you’ll need in the kitchen. These knives are so well balanced, that they can be held with the tip of your finger. With excellent edge retention these knives are engineered to be used daily.

title: Acuto Damascus Steel Chef Knife
body_html: The Acuto Damascus Steel Chef Knife gives off a certain allure from its exquisite pattern, toughness and durability. Handcrafted out of 67 Layers of VG-10 Japanese Damascus Steel, its beautiful design impresses with details of its well-calculated, meticulous style. Visualize your kitchen knives having more aesthetic appeal with their beautiful figure, seriously sharp edge and excellent edge retention. The ebony-wood handle has an ideal size and a very angular profile for superior comfort and control. Kitchen knives with attractive Damascus patterns are at the forefront of the world.

title: Acrylic Tower
body_html:
Gorgeous to look at, more fun to play. Forty-eight clear, frosted, light and dark grey pieces create an ombre effect inside a tall clear acrylic box. With no player limit, this game of delicate balance is great for date nights, dinner parties and total ragers.

Details:

  • Clear solid acrylic box with clear, frosted, light and dark grey solid acrylic pieces

body_html: Get Shade — Illuminate your space with the Alhazen Floor Lamp. body_html:
This product is currently in development. Expect shipping in March 2022

Covered in vegan friendly fur, the Hug Lamp is tactile to the touch and adds a sense of happy coziness to any room. This production version comes with convenient dimmer and switch.

“This design means a lot to me personally as I’ve been separated from my Girlfriend and friends for over 16 months due to travel restrictions” said the designer. “If you are lucky enough to be with your loved ones, treasure these moments you can share together”

title: Forest of Gold Oil Painting
body_html:
"What if other people don’t like it? What if I don’t like it later? I don’t want to make a fool of myself!" Although it’s natural, don’t feel intimidated about buying a piece of art!

According to Professor Semir Zeki’s research, a neurobiologist at the University College London, viewing of art increases dopamine and the activity in brain’s frontal cortex which results in experiencing pleasure similar to as being in romantic love or recreational drug taking. Isn’t that a good enough reason to add few pieces of art to your surroundings?

Some people express themselves through what they wear or what they say, while others collect interesting things that say just as much about themselves. Have fun with it. Nobody's judging.

Details:

  • 3D effects bringing the painting to life
  • Includes wooden frame
  • Size: 75 x 75 x 3.8 cm

title: Pride Rock Lamp
body_html:
Introducing the Pride Rock Lamp - a single, uniquely shaped and astounding art piece that functions more than just a mere lamp. With a Himalayan salt air purifier, it's smooth and sleek design, combined with ideal functionality, make it a must have addition whether on a bed side or desk table.

Say good bye to dull and unpleasing desk lamps. Good bye to switches, chaotic tangled cords, electrical extensions and mess.

Give your walls a coastal feel with the lovely beach-inspired look of this art print. The Boats Hanging Stretched Canvas will be a pleasure to look at every day in your living room, bedroom, office or any room in the home. This is sure to become the focal piece of your home.
